bio.openEndedText: Have been a member on Turo since 2015 but just started this  Turo business in 2022. It has been an amazing experience and I'm looking forward to be better at this business each and every day.

Hello! I'm Josh, and I am your local Memphis Turo Host! I'm a car enthusiast at heart, and enjoy all kinds of cars, trucks, classics, exotics, motorcycles, etc. Turo has allowed me to combine my passion for cars with business, and I hope to build a well diversified fleet of practical, as well as "fun" vehicles along this journey!

I found Turo many years ago during my days serving in the U.S. Navy, when I would be sent away on travel. I always thought it was fun to try new cars, versus getting the "run of the mill" cars that are available from the major car rental companies. 

So, in late 2021, I decided to begin the adventure of being a host!

Thanks for reading my profile, and I hope to have the opportunity to earn your business in the near future!

Sincerely,
Josh

Your Trusted Turo Host,

Greetings, fellow travelers and car enthusiasts!

I'm Curtdell, your dedicated Turo host, and I'm more than just someone renting out a car – I'm your trustworthy companion on the road to exceptional experiences. Allow me to share a little about myself, so you can feel confident and comfortable choosing one of my vehicles for your journey.


Why I’m Responsible and Trustworthy:
Responsibility and trustworthiness are not just words to me; they are the core values that guide my life. I believe in upholding the highest standards of integrity and reliability. As your Turo host, you can count on me to ensure your rental experience is smooth, transparent, and worry-free. Your safety and satisfaction are my top priorities.


My Hobbies and Interests:
In the realm of hobbies, I'm a multifaceted individual. You'll often find me engrossed in the pages of a good book, exploring worlds and ideas through the power of literature. On the court, I embrace the art of hooping, showcasing my skills and agility with every dribble and shot. Sleep is not just a necessity but a cherished pastime, allowing me to recharge and approach each day with renewed vigor. Additionally, I'm deeply passionate about the world of business, constantly seeking opportunities and innovations to fuel my entrepreneurial spirit.


Dream Car - Ferrari 488 Spider:
Ah, the Ferrari 488 Spider – a masterpiece on wheels and my ultimate dream car. Its sleek design, raw power, and unmatched elegance symbolize my aspirations for life's extraordinary experiences. Just as I dream of one day cruising in this marvel, I strive to provide you with a rental experience that is nothing short of exceptional.


Your Journey with Me:
When you choose to rent from me, you're not just getting a car; you're gaining a partner in your adventure. With my dedication to responsibility, my diverse interests, and my dream of a Ferrari 488 Spider fueling my passion for excellence, I invite you to embark on your journey with confidence. Whether you're on a business trip, a family vacation, or a spontaneous road adventure, rest assured that your Turo experience with me will be marked by reliability, transparency, and the pursuit of excellence.

Thank you for considering my vehicles for your travels. I look forward to welcoming you and ensuring your journey is as remarkable and memorable as it deserves to be.

Safe travels and happy driving!

Warm regards,

Curtdell 
Your Trusted Turo Host
